Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船？


Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据名册上记载

Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:47.52,OT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)}原石的觉醒

Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有267人乘坐在这上面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后全都失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船上载著Perseus之像 Euryale之瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:55.27,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perseus 希腊神话中杀死美杜莎的英雄 Euryale希腊神话蛇妖三姐妹之一 美杜莎的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:03:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放一起的两个东西不知道被哪个笨蛋放在了一起啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的对手只靠我们是无法对抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.23,0:03:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须借助那位大人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让他觉醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 这也是为了有马大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…死…死…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别挡路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 全部都白费了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安丹童子同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说若菜啊 别和他打招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话回来啊 怎么偏偏会是他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于那家伙的传闻都没什么好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易有能拿到两万元的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你跑去说一句「去死吧 有马」就可以了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 作为惩罚你要付一万元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们家很有钱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这个没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 你还敢这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}啊 丹童子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在看什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么事吗 丹童子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在这种地方虚度光阴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太没防备了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我邀请你进矿石部这事 你考虑过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}我不加入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回答得太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子同学你不是经常在河边捡石头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天啊 大家要一起去美术馆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边庭院里的石头啊 超可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得丹童子同学你一定会喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以和我们一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.85,0:05:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别说这种话呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 这孩子脑子稍微有点短路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在日出公园门口的车站等你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了啦 若菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}5点半在那里等你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直等你来的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说若菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要去和那种家伙搭话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种男人加入矿石部里的话会很麻烦的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很麻烦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他曾经把混混们都送进医院了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要是发火了不知道会做出什么事来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 那不是传闻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没见过他做过什么坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他啊 经常在河边捡石头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曰「爱石之人绝非恶人」喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路A封锁完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路B封锁完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路C封锁完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 在任务结束前就这样先待机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.13,0:06:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙击班 情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,point alpha 准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,point bravo 准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射击命令由现场发出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等待讯号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 准备已经完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开车过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是丹童子有马先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是蓝羽财团的CEO 蓝羽琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是管家镜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鬼瓦啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望您能将力量借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天在三浦半岛的海面上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一艘大型货船发生爆炸并被烧毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事您知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事是由被我们称为「恶石」的怪物引发的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快 「恶石」将会带来更大的灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打倒它们 我们需要您的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是什么传销的话就请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马先生 请将您沉睡这的力量借给我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是您在三年前所使用的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想隐瞒也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们对于你的事了若指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子有马 17岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新港学园2年级 成绩中等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14岁的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暴力事件中将18名高中生打伤至住院8个月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到了停学半年的处分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在保护观察中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲不明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲在未婚状态下出产
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在十年前由于事故而死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后保护人由…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你们有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是别和我扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马先生 请听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了别管我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ready
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bravo 了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha 了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 糟糕了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙的力量超出了我的想像啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻离开那里啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会被全灭的啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别和我…扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 暂时先撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃 再去找他可能会被杀掉的啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:10:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 最糟糕的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是明户二号大街 怪物正向这边…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口骚动不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很吵闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若菜 真的要等那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能会来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子同学一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「恶石」好像再次开始活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻进入警戒状态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 准备好运输兵和契约装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:55.91,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「恶石」确认 「恶石」确认…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「恶石」在临海公园现身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正向东南方以时速3公里移动中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直升机飞往指定座标
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 请报座标
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,35 point 7719
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,139 point 6361
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约10分钟后到达指定座标
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请小心行事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你发现得晚了啊 鬼瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪有马 对「恶石」的感应变迟钝了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在日出公园门口的车站等你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别和我扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直等著的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动起来！我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口不停地骚动著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜先生 把恶石前进方向上与原石有关的资料发给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我有关这里的更详细资料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 森园美术馆对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.11,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stheno 蛇妖三姐妹之一 美杜莎的另一个姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在Stheno之瞳正在那里展出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可就糟了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美杜莎有两个拥有不死之力的姐姐啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个是Euryale
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个就是Stheno
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美杜莎已经得到了Euryale的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果连Stheno的力量都得到了的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就无能为力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 看起来好贵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说要5亿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且不论庭院里的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有这个我们也来得值了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有通知告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为发生了紧急事态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给大家添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但请避难离开会场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先联络下若菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 扬羽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂断了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 没讯号了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请你们去避难巴士上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路线上的避难状况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在渐渐进行中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stheno之瞳的采购呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出了高于原价两倍的金额
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是持有者却不答应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是提到三倍金额还不答应的话就收手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在美杜莎到达Stheno之瞳前 由我打败它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 镜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了以防万一 去和有马接触
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你还相信那家伙啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换 请带上狙击…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃 你的生命很危险喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能在此拯救他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就失去拥有力量的意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 我也会拼尽全力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要回府邸了 去掩护大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才收到了一条新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像现在横须贺市内发出了特别事态宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市民们开始进行避难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现场的小林记者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底现在情况怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察并没有发出声明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以完全不知道发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如大家所见 从刚才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市内就断断续续冒出火与烟气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你 那边交通管制了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有伤到它一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约装甲 主控系统失效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜先生 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动辅助系统
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「恶石」的状况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正大幅脱离警戒范围进行移动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标变成琉璃了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是想把琉璃和吊坠两个都吃了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为比起Euryale 这块原石更具有力量啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要是吃了琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就真得能成不死之身了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎会让这种事得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖拖拉拉地赶不上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为他会来的说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是 有马先生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 日出町上空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看见美杜莎和丹童子有马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两只恶石交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在5分钟后也能到达了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样给我先待机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐一定会乱来 不快点的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你负责救助伤患和叫救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然恶石不过是恶石吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去自我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许出手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马先生 住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 清醒过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了同样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量会伤害他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么应该消失的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就唤醒你真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒Sacred Seven的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之记忆聚集我身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之意识赐予你身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我…真正的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜先生 Stheno的采购失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个笨蛋持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贪心不足蛇吞象啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个超级大的恶石跳去琉璃你那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 你的「意识」我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.49,0:21:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得找个无人区
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马 同时破坏那两个核心啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时破坏两个的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:21:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给老子粉碎吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑震荡？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.31,0:22:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其他都是些擦伤真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.07,0:22:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 丹童子要是再来早一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 只要他来了 我就OK了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得他好像肯加入矿石部了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.48,0:23:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别做这种无聊事了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.45,0:23:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…谢谢你 丹童子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 果然来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.37,0:23:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然居然 今天还有别的想要入部的人也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们认识？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.38,0:23:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能跟有马先生在一起所以我入部了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你们不是这里的学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.27,0:24:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天开始 我是这个学校的学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.79,0:24:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位大人是理事长
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.95,0:24:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我怕麻烦啦 所以就把学校给买下了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.83,0:24:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.70,0:24:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES 真的啊鬼

